      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SPRING BRUMBY (1) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner (22.87) three back at Geelong. Has the ability and can find winning form this time. PAW ELODEE (4) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, rewarded with a win last time at Ballarat over 390m. Expecting another bold showing. AUSSIE WAGYU (7) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at Ballarat over 390m behind Paw Sapphire (22.46) in a Grade 5. Scored at his previous run. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Can figure in the finish. TOOTSIE (2) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
